          <p>
            <xref ref="EQUATIONExpIVP2">IVP</xref> has the initial condition, <m>y(0)=1.</m> Plot the
            point <m>(0,1)</m> and use this slope field to sketch the solution of
            <xref ref="EQUATIONExpIVP2">IVP</xref>. Compare your solution with the  approximation
            we obtained in <xref ref="SECTIONEulersMethod"></xref>. Do they look like
            the same solution?
          </p>
        </statement>
</problem>

      <exercise>
        <introduction>
